1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,960
Rituals, beliefs, and myths in this series are a work of fiction and in no regard refer to religions or faiths of any certain cultures.

2
00:00:14,240 --> 00:00:15,640
A soul binding ritual?

3
00:00:15,640 --> 00:00:17,320
When two souls are bound,

4
00:00:17,480 --> 00:00:20,640
half of a person’s spiritual energy
will flow into the other.

5
00:00:20,720 --> 00:00:23,000
And it will protect you from now on.

6
00:00:24,960 --> 00:00:27,120
You all need to know that in the last stretch
right before we seal it,

7
00:00:27,120 --> 00:00:29,640
the demon will make its last-gasp attempt.

8
00:00:34,760 --> 00:00:37,920
Qi Rong’s strongest power is
his manipulation of fog.

9
00:00:38,120 --> 00:00:39,520
Whatever happens,

10
00:00:39,520 --> 00:00:41,440
we have to continue with the ritual.

11
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:19,080
What are you standing still for?

12
00:01:19,960 --> 00:01:22,960
When in my battlefield,

13
00:01:22,960 --> 00:01:27,320
everyone must face their worst enemy.

14
00:01:41,320 --> 00:01:42,400
You are…

15
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:44,600
Who I am

16
00:01:45,240 --> 00:01:47,160
matters no more than who you are.

17
00:01:48,360 --> 00:01:50,759
To get through this door,

18
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:54,320
you must prove your clairvoyance.

19
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:57,160
I don’t have time for this.

20
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:15,320
Now that’s a really good liquor.

21
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:20,640
A WORTHLESS PUPPET
- Lapdog!
- Lapdog!

22
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:22,760
- Lapdog!
- Lapdog!

23
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:23,400
LAPDOG!

24
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:26,680
- Lapdog!
- Lapdog!

25
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:31,840
We’re locked in here by the demon.

26
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,560
The only way to clear this fog

27
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:36,320
is to give the demon a sacrifice.

28
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:54,720
Is your worst enemy

29
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:57,120
simply these mirrors?

30
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:40,400
You again?

31
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:43,920
Alright.

32
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,960
Let’s decide once and for all.

33
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:06,240
Lapdog!

34
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:08,200
Scumbag!

35
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:10,360
Worthless!

36
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:11,120
Lapdog!

37
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:13,000
Get out!

38
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:13,920
Lapdog!

39
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,320
Scumbag!

40
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,440
Worthless!

41
00:05:26,440 --> 00:05:27,080
Lapdog!

42
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:17,680
For the only path to your destination,

43
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:21,920
you must prove your clairvoyance.

44
00:06:47,159 --> 00:06:47,960
Pete.

45
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:49,520
Are you serious?

46
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:51,400
Hell yeah.

47
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,680
Why would I lie?

48
00:06:55,600 --> 00:07:00,840
One of us has to be sacrificed
to lift this fog.

49
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:04,480
If you won’t do it,

50
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,760
someone else will be sacrificed.

51
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:10,720
You know damn well how important
they all are to this ritual.

52
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,320
Now choose who will die.

53
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:18,560
How’d we even choose that?

54
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,000
Would you rather I choose?

55
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:21,600
Well?

56
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,000
Maybe you?

57
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:23,920
Or you?

58
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:26,800
Crap!

59
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:28,200
I’ll do it.

60
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,360
- Jack.
- Jack.

61
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:34,440
I’ll do it.

62
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:37,159
If it means everyone else gets to live,

63
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:38,720
I’ll die.

64
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:44,320
You

65
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:47,440
who spent his whole life studying heaven.

66
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:49,840
Do you know

67
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:56,640
whether heaven is what you observe,
or what observes you?

68
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:00,120
Heaven

69
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:03,640
decides the fate of all things.

70
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:06,080
Heaven is above all things.

71
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,440
Heaven observes us.

72
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,480
We do not observe heaven.

73
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:19,680
What resides above heaven?

74
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:22,160
Nothing does.

75
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:22,880
Fool!

76
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:35,400
Your eyes study the texts,

77
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:38,159
but you do not understand the message.

78
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:42,039
You are not worthy of this eye.

79
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:51,920
What a shame

80
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:57,600
that the likes of you are lauded as a seer.

81
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:06,840
How come when you tell them
to wait for light

82
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:12,640
they’re always left behind
to die in the dark?

83
00:09:14,800 --> 00:09:16,720
Because no one knows
what heaven has in mind.

84
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:18,800
All things

85
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:22,440
are as heaven dictates.

86
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:24,760
You are not worthy of
the leg that carries you!

87
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:34,680
Is there no way, Master?

88
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:36,280
That’s what it shows on the trigrams.

89
00:09:36,760 --> 00:09:38,440
I only tell you what the book says.

90
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,640
Honestly, Master,

91
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,560
have you ever gotten anything right?

92
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:47,840
Under heaven, you are incompetent
in reading fortunes,

93
00:09:50,160 --> 00:09:51,760
but in this battlefield,

94
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:55,080
I will grant you the gift of clairvoyance.

95
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,320
Now divine

96
00:09:58,840 --> 00:10:00,600
whether you and your friends

97
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:03,920
will make it out of this battle alive.

98
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:09,720
And I will make sure it happens.

99
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:45,800
What a good liquor.

100
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,400
What the hell is this?

101
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:33,520
(Life is meaningless.)

102
00:11:33,520 --> 00:11:35,320
(Ideology. Duty.)

103
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:37,600
(Good. Evil.)

104
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:40,560
(Nothing is true in the end.)

105
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:50,120
Lapdog!

106
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,040
Disgrace!

107
00:11:51,040 --> 00:11:52,920
Reconsider your decision

108
00:11:52,920 --> 00:11:55,920
or never call yourself Wu ever again.

109
00:11:56,680 --> 00:11:57,880
Is this all my teaching has led you to?

110
00:11:57,880 --> 00:11:59,720
It was all my fault.

111
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:00,960
Heaven will always punish
those who are unnatural.

112
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:02,680
What a disappointment.

113
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:05,400
It was my fault. I did not teach you well.

114
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:08,280
Our ancestors gave us one duty;

115
00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:10,440
to protect heaven and nature.

116
00:12:11,040 --> 00:12:13,880
Lapdog!

117
00:12:49,800 --> 00:12:50,880
What does it say?

118
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:54,880
Will we make it?

119
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:59,000
The lower trigram is ‘kun.’

120
00:12:59,480 --> 00:13:01,200
The upper trigram is ‘qian.’

121
00:13:02,280 --> 00:13:04,480
The whole hexagram is…

122
00:13:05,640 --> 00:13:06,600
‘Pi.’

123
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,400
What does that mean?

124
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:14,280
We’re going to fail.

125
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:21,600
I mean, your prediction
is never accurate anyway, right?

126
00:13:23,560 --> 00:13:24,760
Hey, don’t laugh.

127
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:34,800
Why did you stop?

128
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:41,080
You yearn for accuracy, do you not?

129
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:45,040
I will grant you what you want.

130
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:47,440
Now divine.

131
00:13:47,920 --> 00:13:49,280
Divine your future.

132
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:56,720
Otherwise, I will be the one
who decides your fate.

133
00:15:07,840 --> 00:15:09,680
The sound of the drum has gone silent.

134
00:15:10,880 --> 00:15:13,960
Your friends are defeated.

135
00:15:14,040 --> 00:15:17,480
And you are the only one who
has not put up a fight.

136
00:15:19,480 --> 00:15:23,000
Make an effort, you outcast!

137
00:15:23,760 --> 00:15:26,520
Try and find a way out of this.

138
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:31,800
The harder you try,
the more lost you will be.

139
00:15:32,160 --> 00:15:34,160
So this is your true fate…

140
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:37,800
To be confined with your
own reflection for all eternity.

141
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:47,560
At this point, it is undeniable

142
00:15:48,760 --> 00:15:49,960
that what we’re going to do

143
00:15:50,920 --> 00:15:52,080
is nothing short of life-threatening.

144
00:15:53,760 --> 00:15:56,320
If anyone wants to back out now,

145
00:16:00,920 --> 00:16:01,520
just say the word.

146
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:08,640
If we back out right now,

147
00:16:09,120 --> 00:16:10,280
that means

148
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:12,640
the demon has already won, doesn’t it?

149
00:16:20,280 --> 00:16:20,640
No.

150
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:22,880
We will win.

151
00:16:25,480 --> 00:16:29,400
You don’t even dare move your leg

152
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:31,840
and you think you’ll still find your way out?

153
00:16:35,040 --> 00:16:36,680
I am not here to find a way out.

154
00:16:38,640 --> 00:16:40,160
I am here to seal you.

155
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:46,680
You think we’re stupid, huh?

156
00:16:56,640 --> 00:17:00,040
And right now, I am waiting,

157
00:17:13,839 --> 00:17:14,720
waiting for my friends

158
00:17:18,040 --> 00:17:19,599
to stand together again.

159
00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:01,960
The last set of divination:

160
00:18:02,800 --> 00:18:06,080
yang has moved into yin.

161
00:18:07,480 --> 00:18:11,240
As dictated by Hexagram 12
changing into Hexagram 45.

162
00:18:13,760 --> 00:18:15,600
The path may begin with difficulties,

163
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:19,840
but it will end in success.

164
00:18:20,640 --> 00:18:22,280
You haven’t taken a look at the last coin.

165
00:18:26,000 --> 00:18:26,920
I don’t need to look.

166
00:18:28,600 --> 00:18:29,480
Because I’ve seen it.

167
00:18:32,040 --> 00:18:33,600
The clearest I’ve ever seen
in my entire life.

168
00:18:41,320 --> 00:18:41,920
You!

169
00:18:56,560 --> 00:18:58,040
When yang is deterred from earth,

170
00:18:58,520 --> 00:18:59,560
and yin is oppressed,

171
00:18:59,560 --> 00:19:01,680
and a tremendous force
of energy accumulates,

172
00:19:02,040 --> 00:19:03,040
thus is born Earth yao.

173
00:19:04,040 --> 00:19:05,760
When there is too much yin
in a body of water,

174
00:19:05,760 --> 00:19:06,800
and yang is out of balance,

175
00:19:06,920 --> 00:19:08,120
thus is born Water yao.

176
00:19:08,840 --> 00:19:13,320
An abnormally strong storm is often caused by the power of Air and Fire yao.

177
00:19:14,520 --> 00:19:15,320
Don’t you find it strange

178
00:19:16,120 --> 00:19:18,760
that we were taught that yao is unnatural?

179
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:22,880
But if you look closely at it,
it is, in itself, nature.

180
00:19:23,560 --> 00:19:24,440
You wanna sell that?

181
00:19:25,280 --> 00:19:27,640
The bracelet that seals all yao elementals.

182
00:19:28,160 --> 00:19:29,200
I bet it’ll fetch you a heavy sum.

183
00:19:30,080 --> 00:19:30,400
No.

184
00:19:31,680 --> 00:19:32,520
I’m keeping it.

185
00:19:34,160 --> 00:19:36,080
On this path I chose,

186
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:40,080
so many backs will turn on me.

187
00:19:41,240 --> 00:19:43,120
But I will always have
the force of nature by my side,

188
00:19:44,080 --> 00:19:45,040
protecting me.

189
00:20:16,920 --> 00:20:18,400
Will you promise me one thing?

190
00:20:20,400 --> 00:20:22,640
Will you try to get the demon
out of my body?

191
00:20:24,160 --> 00:20:25,920
If a solution ever presents itself one day,

192
00:20:28,040 --> 00:20:29,760
I want you to do it.

193
00:20:31,360 --> 00:20:31,720
Why?

194
00:20:32,960 --> 00:20:34,680
You finally learned to live with it now.

195
00:20:35,480 --> 00:20:38,040
More importantly, you have its power.

196
00:20:38,400 --> 00:20:39,920
It’s still a demon.

197
00:20:45,720 --> 00:20:46,160
Pete.

198
00:20:48,240 --> 00:20:49,920
You shouldn’t think of it as a curse.

199
00:20:52,360 --> 00:20:53,960
However it was put inside you,

200
00:20:55,120 --> 00:20:56,960
it was given to you by your parents

201
00:20:58,360 --> 00:20:59,680
to help you overcome your disability,

202
00:21:01,200 --> 00:21:02,760
and to give you a
fair chance at a better life.

203
00:21:09,120 --> 00:21:10,320
You should think of it as a blessing,

204
00:21:11,800 --> 00:21:13,160
and a part of who you are.

205
00:22:39,720 --> 00:22:40,840
Let me give you some advice.

206
00:22:41,600 --> 00:22:42,600
When reading fortunes,

207
00:22:43,600 --> 00:22:45,040
you can’t just be by the book.

208
00:22:47,200 --> 00:22:48,480
You need to read from here.

209
00:22:50,840 --> 00:22:54,280
This is where heaven
communicates with you.

210
00:23:06,360 --> 00:23:08,080
Damn it!

211
00:23:16,000 --> 00:23:17,920
(Heaven favors balances.)

212
00:23:18,600 --> 00:23:20,920
(No matter how powerful a demon is,)

213
00:23:21,480 --> 00:23:23,880
(it cannot be stronger than a human’s will.)

214
00:23:24,560 --> 00:23:29,320
(That’s why demons
make you question your own will.)

215
00:23:30,360 --> 00:23:33,800
(You don’t need to fall for its ploy.)

216
00:23:45,920 --> 00:23:46,680
Pete.

217
00:23:54,040 --> 00:23:55,600
Where’s Niran?

218
00:24:00,880 --> 00:24:07,560
Do you mean to say you’re willing
to be confined here forever?

219
00:24:12,240 --> 00:24:13,680
We can’t keep waiting.

220
00:24:13,680 --> 00:24:15,600
We need to carry on with the ritual.

221
00:24:23,320 --> 00:24:25,360
I’m just scared

222
00:24:26,720 --> 00:24:28,600
that it might defeat me again,

223
00:24:29,720 --> 00:24:32,080
and I’d lose everyone I have.

224
00:24:38,200 --> 00:24:40,560
But you have me now, Pete.

225
00:24:42,000 --> 00:24:44,360
I won’t let that happen.

226
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:45,920
You know that.

227
00:24:46,920 --> 00:24:49,880
I will never disappear from you.

228
00:25:01,720 --> 00:25:05,080
Blow out the light in front of you.

229
00:25:14,000 --> 00:25:17,360
Put an end to this ritual.

230
00:25:19,840 --> 00:25:22,640
You and I will be free.

231
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:24,640
Otherwise…

232
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:28,320
you will be sealed along with me.

233
00:25:43,760 --> 00:25:44,400
No

234
00:25:44,880 --> 00:25:46,320
You will be sealed alone!

235
00:25:47,960 --> 00:25:48,760
As for me,

236
00:25:49,840 --> 00:25:51,760
I’m going back to my friends.

237
00:25:52,640 --> 00:25:54,200
You!

238
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:35,120
Did you pull me back?

239
00:26:35,840 --> 00:26:37,760
Just as you did.

240
00:26:40,320 --> 00:26:42,240
Everyone’s here now.

241
00:26:42,600 --> 00:26:44,520
You’re the last one to show up.

242
00:26:50,760 --> 00:26:51,840
To think that

243
00:26:52,800 --> 00:26:55,160
I was the only person who got lost.

244
00:26:57,720 --> 00:27:02,600
I didn’t expect that this bond
would really save me.

245
00:27:06,160 --> 00:27:11,040
But you sure learned
how to use its power quickly.

246
00:27:11,520 --> 00:27:13,400
I didn’t learn jack

247
00:27:15,560 --> 00:27:17,200
All I did was think of you

248
00:27:18,000 --> 00:27:19,640
and the thread did its job.

249
00:27:22,680 --> 00:27:24,800
Since our souls are bound to each other,

250
00:27:26,520 --> 00:27:28,640
if you’re ever in trouble again,

251
00:27:29,600 --> 00:27:31,720
why don’t you try thinking of me?

252
00:27:32,360 --> 00:27:34,160
I’ll be there to save you.

253
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:42,080
You’re not alone, Niran.

254
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:45,520
You have me.

255
00:27:49,120 --> 00:27:51,000
You have us.

256
00:28:24,640 --> 00:28:25,920
Now…

257
00:28:26,200 --> 00:28:28,800
Are you ready to come back
and defeat this demon?

258
00:28:47,240 --> 00:28:49,200
Storms subsided

259
00:28:49,200 --> 00:28:50,440
Chaos resolved.

260
00:28:50,440 --> 00:28:51,720
The power of evil,

261
00:28:51,720 --> 00:28:54,080
be sealed!

262
00:29:11,040 --> 00:29:13,040
Qi Rong, be sealed!

263
00:29:13,040 --> 00:29:14,320
- Be sealed!
- Be sealed!

264
00:29:36,280 --> 00:29:37,560
Lord Warrior?

265
00:30:11,760 --> 00:30:13,800
What do you want?

266
00:30:14,240 --> 00:30:15,360
Money?

267
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:16,920
I’ll give you anything.

268
00:30:17,560 --> 00:30:18,680
10 million?

269
00:30:18,840 --> 00:30:20,080
Will 10 million suffice

270
00:30:20,760 --> 00:30:23,120
I’ll give the first person
who steps out 10 million!

271
00:30:24,480 --> 00:30:25,520
What do I want?

272
00:30:25,520 --> 00:30:26,480
Don’t talk to him!

273
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:28,920
What I want is my sister’s life spirit back.

274
00:30:29,400 --> 00:30:30,920
And I’ll beat your ass later!

275
00:30:33,720 --> 00:30:34,720
Is that right?

276
00:30:35,360 --> 00:30:39,000
So those Suming bastards
didn’t tell you the truth, then?

277
00:30:40,720 --> 00:30:41,120
What?

278
00:30:41,960 --> 00:30:43,240
Don’t you know

279
00:30:43,960 --> 00:30:46,240
that this ritual you’re performing

280
00:30:46,960 --> 00:30:49,240
won’t simply seal Lord Warrior?

281
00:30:49,840 --> 00:30:51,840
It will suppress all life spirits with him,

282
00:30:51,840 --> 00:30:53,760
including your sister’s!

283
00:30:53,760 --> 00:30:55,440
They lied to you, you fool!

284
00:30:56,240 --> 00:30:58,000
You can’t save your sister, you idiot!

285
00:30:58,000 --> 00:30:58,760
You freaking idiot!

286
00:30:58,760 --> 00:30:59,160
Damn you!

287
00:31:02,080 --> 00:31:03,160
What does he mean, Niran?

288
00:31:04,760 --> 00:31:07,240
Evil General, accept your confinedment!

289
00:31:08,360 --> 00:31:10,200
I’m asking you what he means, Niran!

290
00:31:10,840 --> 00:31:11,960
What does he mean?

291
00:31:15,360 --> 00:31:16,480
What does he mean?

292
00:31:16,840 --> 00:31:18,280
Answer me, you jerk!

293
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:20,200
Let go of me!

294
00:31:20,280 --> 00:31:21,120
Stop, Niran!

295
00:31:21,120 --> 00:31:21,360
Pete!

296
00:31:21,360 --> 00:31:21,960
I said answer me, Niran!

297
00:31:22,080 --> 00:31:22,320
Pete!

298
00:31:22,320 --> 00:31:23,000
Answer me, you jerk!

299
00:31:26,240 --> 00:31:27,320
Did you lie to me, Niran?

300
00:31:30,640 --> 00:31:35,040
Qi Rong, be sealed!

301
00:31:44,360 --> 00:31:45,160
Let go of me!

302
00:31:46,440 --> 00:31:47,920
Did you lie to me?

303
00:31:51,080 --> 00:31:52,040
Tell me

304
00:31:52,960 --> 00:31:54,880
what Li Puo said wasn’t true.

305
00:31:57,600 --> 00:31:59,680
He was just messing with me, wasn’t he?

306
00:32:00,680 --> 00:32:02,360
He was lying, wasn’t he?

307
00:32:04,040 --> 00:32:07,560
Is my sister safe now?

308
00:32:20,760 --> 00:32:22,360
Answer me!

309
00:32:23,080 --> 00:32:24,360
We might not have saved your sister,

310
00:32:24,600 --> 00:32:25,640
but we’ve saved a thousand more.

311
00:32:25,640 --> 00:32:27,240
I don’t give a damn about that

312
00:32:33,120 --> 00:32:34,840
Why did you lie to me?

313
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:38,920
Did you lie to me?

314
00:32:42,960 --> 00:32:45,040
What the hell do you take me for?

315
00:32:48,600 --> 00:32:50,000
Shit!

316
00:32:50,240 --> 00:32:50,920
You bastard!

317
00:33:19,680 --> 00:33:20,320
Don’t touch me!

318
00:33:38,360 --> 00:33:39,000
Hey!

319
00:33:40,000 --> 00:33:41,360
What the hell did you do, Niran?

320
00:34:14,159 --> 00:34:15,960
He did not lie to you, Pete.

321
00:34:18,199 --> 00:34:20,000
He lied to us.

322
00:34:21,679 --> 00:34:24,600
Your sister is awake now.

323
00:34:36,719 --> 00:34:37,520
Pete

324
00:34:37,840 --> 00:34:38,560
Ploy

325
00:34:47,760 --> 00:34:49,960
You’re alright now.

326
00:34:54,080 --> 00:34:55,320
You’re safe now.

327
00:35:05,520 --> 00:35:07,640
The demon was sealed once.

328
00:35:08,680 --> 00:35:10,800
Although for a short time,

329
00:35:10,800 --> 00:35:12,920
that still weakened it.

330
00:35:13,040 --> 00:35:15,320
When Niran destroyed the seal,

331
00:35:15,600 --> 00:35:18,480
the life spirits that were sealed alongside it

332
00:35:18,480 --> 00:35:21,800
took this chance when the demon’s weakened to get back to their bodies.

333
00:35:26,040 --> 00:35:29,360
But that means the demon roams free,

334
00:35:30,640 --> 00:35:33,360
and it can grow stronger.

335
00:35:42,120 --> 00:35:46,480
The ongoing political crisis
has no solution in sight.

336
00:35:47,800 --> 00:35:48,480
Get out

337
00:35:48,520 --> 00:35:49,120
Get out

338
00:35:49,120 --> 00:35:52,680
DISSOLVE THE PARLIAMENT
The demonstrations all around the country
have been intensified.

339
00:35:52,680 --> 00:35:55,920
SAY NO TO CORRUPTED DEMOCRACY
12 city halls have been set on fire.

340
00:35:55,920 --> 00:36:01,440
FIRE SET BY PROTESTERS
So far, the casualties from this
political turmoil have climbed to 45.

341
00:36:01,440 --> 00:36:02,960
ANALYSTS SUGGEST RESIGNATION WILL NOT RESOLVE CRISIS
I have to be honest.

342
00:36:02,960 --> 00:36:04,920
ANALYSTS SUGGEST RESIGNATION WILL NOT RESOLVE CRISIS
The situation has officially gotten out of hand.

343
00:36:04,920 --> 00:36:06,280
Even if the Prime Minister resigns now,

344
00:36:06,280 --> 00:36:08,560
I doubt it would stop anything.

345
00:36:12,360 --> 00:36:13,440
Get yourself together

346
00:36:14,440 --> 00:36:15,880
and think about what you did.

347
00:36:22,760 --> 00:36:24,920
We can probably find
another chance to seal it.

348
00:36:25,240 --> 00:36:26,440
You really think so?

349
00:36:27,800 --> 00:36:30,040
You think Li Puo won’t do anything?

350
00:37:13,960 --> 00:37:15,480
How’s your sister?

351
00:37:17,160 --> 00:37:22,760
“The doctor said she can go home
after one more night.”

352
00:37:26,440 --> 00:37:26,920
That’s good.

353
00:37:40,400 --> 00:37:46,000
I know you must be disappointed right now
that your plan fell through.

354
00:37:47,800 --> 00:37:50,000
But thank you

355
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:53,400
for saving my sister.

356
00:37:57,480 --> 00:38:00,880
I swear I’ll do anything to help you.

357
00:38:02,360 --> 00:38:04,400
I’ll pay you back for this.

358
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:07,560
Even if I have to die for you,

359
00:38:08,080 --> 00:38:08,760
I’ll do it.

360
00:38:09,880 --> 00:38:11,480
Trust me, Niran.

361
00:38:14,120 --> 00:38:15,720
You really can trust me.

362
00:39:13,280 --> 00:39:14,400
Niran?

363
00:39:14,400 --> 00:39:14,880
Hey!

364
00:39:15,240 --> 00:39:16,000
Niran, what’s wrong?

365
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:16,760
Shit!

366
00:39:17,520 --> 00:39:18,280
Niran?

367
00:39:18,520 --> 00:39:19,280
Niran!

368
00:39:19,840 --> 00:39:20,880
Hey! What’s wrong?

369
00:39:26,000 --> 00:39:27,040
Niran, wake up

370
00:39:27,520 --> 00:39:28,560
What’s happened

371
00:39:28,960 --> 00:39:30,000
Niran!

372
00:39:33,680 --> 00:39:35,120
May your life spirit drift away

373
00:39:36,000 --> 00:39:38,160
and be lost for all eternity,

374
00:39:38,680 --> 00:39:39,400
Niran.

375
00:40:12,120 --> 00:40:14,000
I’ll save you, Niran.

376
00:40:15,320 --> 00:40:17,200
I’ll make good on that promise.

377
00:40:22,640 --> 00:40:24,440
The doctors ran all the tests they could.

378
00:40:24,440 --> 00:40:26,320
But they didn’t find anything
wrong with him.

379
00:40:26,760 --> 00:40:28,360
Then what happened to him?

380
00:40:28,360 --> 00:40:30,760
He’s just like my sister
when she was unconscious.

381
00:40:31,600 --> 00:40:32,880
What I know is that…

382
00:40:32,880 --> 00:40:35,080
The human soul is separated
into two parts:

383
00:40:35,600 --> 00:40:37,080
First is the life spirit,

384
00:40:37,080 --> 00:40:38,960
which represents yang.

385
00:40:39,320 --> 00:40:41,360
This connects with your core,

386
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:42,480
intelligence,

387
00:40:42,480 --> 00:40:44,520
personality, and life purpose.

388
00:40:45,640 --> 00:40:49,000
The yin and yang parts of the soul
are generally always intertwined.

389
00:40:49,840 --> 00:40:53,440
But now that Niran’s life spirit
is severed from his soul…

390
00:40:53,440 --> 00:40:55,880
He’s left with the yin part of the soul,

391
00:40:55,880 --> 00:40:58,080
which controls the body.

392
00:40:58,720 --> 00:41:01,320
It’s exactly what happened to Ploy, Pete.

393
00:41:04,000 --> 00:41:05,800
If Ploy could come back,

394
00:41:05,800 --> 00:41:07,080
Niran can, too.

395
00:41:07,680 --> 00:41:09,280
I don’t think it compares.

396
00:41:09,480 --> 00:41:13,200
Your sister’s life spirit was
devoured by Qi Rong.

397
00:41:16,440 --> 00:41:18,480
That was why it could not
return to the body.

398
00:41:18,480 --> 00:41:20,800
But when the demon was weakened,

399
00:41:21,120 --> 00:41:23,440
the life spirits were released,

400
00:41:23,600 --> 00:41:25,920
and they could return to their bodies.

401
00:41:26,120 --> 00:41:28,440
As for Niran

402
00:41:28,600 --> 00:41:29,880
He was attacked by

403
00:41:29,880 --> 00:41:31,800
a life spirit-cutting ritual.

404
00:41:33,160 --> 00:41:34,280
A life spirit-cutting ritual?

405
00:41:34,280 --> 00:41:36,440
Niran’s life spirit has
drifted away from his body,

406
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:39,600
floating aimlessly around
in the Life Spirit Realm.

407
00:41:40,520 --> 00:41:43,320
Can we at least perform
a ritual to beckon it back?

408
00:41:45,560 --> 00:41:48,560
The Life Spirit Realm is much greater

409
00:41:48,560 --> 00:41:50,480
and more limitless than ours.

410
00:41:51,280 --> 00:41:54,960
Even if we beckon it,
it doesn’t guarantee that he will hear us.

411
00:41:56,840 --> 00:41:58,680
Is there really no way?

412
00:41:58,920 --> 00:42:01,480
Are we supposed to just
leave Niran like this?

413
00:42:02,800 --> 00:42:06,200
There has to be a way to bring him back.

414
00:42:06,640 --> 00:42:08,640
There is.

415
00:42:09,320 --> 00:42:11,600
But the only person who can save Niran

416
00:42:12,560 --> 00:42:13,800
is you.

417
00:42:16,200 --> 00:42:20,360
The silver lining in this situation is that
Niran’s soul is bound to yours.

418
00:42:20,920 --> 00:42:25,520
We can use that connection as a path
to trace Niran’s life spirit.

419
00:42:25,880 --> 00:42:27,040
Only that…

420
00:42:27,200 --> 00:42:30,680
You have to look for him
in the Life Spirit Realm.

421
00:42:30,960 --> 00:42:32,880
You mean he must detach
his own life spirit?

422
00:42:32,880 --> 00:42:34,440
But that is extremely dangerous.

423
00:42:35,680 --> 00:42:37,760
That’s why I’m asking you, Pete,

424
00:42:38,240 --> 00:42:41,240
if you’re willing to risk your life for this.

425
00:42:41,440 --> 00:42:42,280
Yes.

426
00:42:42,720 --> 00:42:43,600
Pete.

427
00:42:43,600 --> 00:42:45,400
It really is dangerous.

428
00:42:45,400 --> 00:42:47,720
Niran is like this because
he saved my sister.

429
00:42:48,360 --> 00:42:51,400
Whatever I have to go up against
or what I have to risk,

430
00:42:52,520 --> 00:42:54,400
I’ll get Niran back.

431
00:42:57,680 --> 00:42:59,120
I’ll do it.

432
00:43:28,560 --> 00:43:31,520
It’s not that I didn’t know what
the soul binding ritual entails.

433
00:43:32,040 --> 00:43:37,640
You think I should just let
the demon devour you like that?

434
00:43:40,920 --> 00:43:41,920
It’s because of you.

435
00:43:41,920 --> 00:43:42,320
Oh?

436
00:43:42,560 --> 00:43:43,640
You made me like this.

437
00:43:43,960 --> 00:43:44,600
The hell, man?

438
00:43:44,600 --> 00:43:45,840
Why are you blaming me?

439
00:43:46,880 --> 00:43:48,520
If we weren’t friends in the first place,

440
00:43:49,120 --> 00:43:50,920
I wouldn’t have to care about you so much.

441
00:43:55,880 --> 00:43:56,680
I see.

442
00:43:57,080 --> 00:43:59,840
So you’re saying I’ve made
your heart feel again?

443
00:44:02,520 --> 00:44:03,160
Ew!

444
00:44:03,600 --> 00:44:04,800
What the hell are you saying?

445
00:44:04,800 --> 00:44:05,720
Well.

446
00:44:06,080 --> 00:44:08,280
You used to be so heartless.

447
00:44:08,480 --> 00:44:10,600
But you’re not anymore.

448
00:44:10,600 --> 00:44:12,760
You care about your friends.

449
00:44:12,880 --> 00:44:14,520
You actually give a damn about people.

450
00:44:14,720 --> 00:44:15,440
See?

451
00:44:15,720 --> 00:44:17,200
This is all my doing.

452
00:44:17,720 --> 00:44:18,120
Huh.

453
00:44:19,920 --> 00:44:22,040
Don’t look so proud of yourself.

454
00:44:24,240 --> 00:44:25,280
But I’ll say…

455
00:44:26,240 --> 00:44:28,840
You’re never heartless from the beginning.

456
00:44:31,960 --> 00:44:33,400
You’re just a tsundere.

457
00:44:33,400 --> 00:44:34,160
You jerk.

458
00:44:34,160 --> 00:44:35,400
See? You’re doing it again.

459
00:44:35,920 --> 00:44:36,720
I’m not a tsundere

460
00:44:36,720 --> 00:44:38,320
You are. You’re being a tsundere right now!

461
00:44:38,760 --> 00:44:39,600
You idiot.

462
00:44:39,600 --> 00:44:40,880
You’re still doing it.

463
00:44:40,880 --> 00:44:41,720
I’m not a tsundere.

464
00:44:41,720 --> 00:44:42,080
You are, too.

465
00:44:42,720 --> 00:44:43,600
This is just my face.

466
00:44:43,600 --> 00:44:45,600
This is how I look, you jerk.

467
00:44:47,640 --> 00:44:49,560
Exactly something a tsundere would say.

468
00:44:49,560 --> 00:44:50,800
You should knock it off.

469
00:44:50,800 --> 00:44:52,800
Shut your mouth and eat your vegetables.

470
00:44:53,200 --> 00:44:55,200
Shut your mouth and eat your vegetables.

471
00:44:59,880 --> 00:45:04,280
The Life Spirit Realm is vast
and moves as fast as one’s thought

472
00:45:04,280 --> 00:45:06,800
Niran is lost in that world.

473
00:45:06,800 --> 00:45:08,280
When you find him,

474
00:45:08,280 --> 00:45:10,640
you must do whatever it takes
to make him trust you.

475
00:45:10,800 --> 00:45:11,560
Do I know you?

476
00:45:11,560 --> 00:45:12,280
It’s me, Pete.

477
00:45:12,280 --> 00:45:13,120
I don’t know you!

478
00:45:13,560 --> 00:45:13,880
Shit!

479
00:45:13,880 --> 00:45:14,400
Outta my way!

480
00:45:15,040 --> 00:45:16,320
You have only eight hours in that realm.

481
00:45:16,360 --> 00:45:19,680
Otherwise, you won’t be able
to leave forever.

482
00:45:20,400 --> 00:45:21,960
Come back with me.

483
00:45:21,960 --> 00:45:23,920
Come back to your real life.
